   "file": "earth.zil",
   "line": 69,
   "endLine": 76,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-HOUSEWRECK ()\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,BEDROOM ,FRONT-PORCH>\n\t\t<TELL CR\n\"Astoundingly, a \" D ,BULLDOZER \" pokes through your wall. However, you have\nno time for surprise because the ceiling is collapsing on you as\">\n\t\t<BETTER-LUCK>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
