   "file": "earth.zil",
   "line": 282,
   "endLine": 287,
   "source": "<ROUTINE CURTAINS-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? OPEN LOOK-INSIDE>\n\t\t<FCLEAR ,BULLDOZER ,INVISIBLE>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"As you part \" D ,CURTAINS \" you see that i\" ,NICE-DAY \", and a large yellow \"\nD ,BULLDOZER \" is advancing on \" D ,HOME \".\" CR>)>>"
