   "source": "<ROUTINE PUB-OBJECT-F ()\n\t <COND (<VERB? WALK-TO THROUGH>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,PUB>\n\t\t       <TELL ,LOOK-AROUND CR>)\n\t\t      (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,COUNTRY-LANE>\n\t\t       <DO-WALK ,P?WEST>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <V-WALK-AROUND>)>)\n\t       (<VERB? EXIT LEAVE DISEMBARK>\n\t\t<COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,PUB>\n\t\t       <DO-WALK ,P?EAST>)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <TELL ,LOOK-AROUND CR>)>)>>"
