   "source": "<ROUTINE SAY-HERE ()\n\t <COND (<ZERO? ,LIT>\n\t\t<TELL \"Darkness\">)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL D ,HERE>\n\t        <COND (<G? ,WIDTH 74>\n\t\t       <COND (<IN? ,PROTAGONIST ,POETRY-APPRECIATION-CHAIR>\n\t\t\t      <TELL \", in the chair\">)       \n\t\t\t     (<NOT <IN? ,PROTAGONIST ,HERE>>\n\t\t              <TELL \", in the \" D <LOC ,PROTAGONIST>>)\n\t\t\t     (,LYING-DOWN\n\t\t\t      <TELL \", lying down\">)>)>)>\n\t <RTRUE>>"
