   "file": "unearth.zil",
   "line": 774,
   "endLine": 776,
   "source": "<ROUTINE PARTY-DESC (ROOM)\n\t <TELL \"You are in a large \" D .ROOM\n\". There is a party going on. Other rooms lie to the \">>"
