   "source": "<ROUTINE V-BOARD (\"AUX\" AV)\n\t <COND (<FSET? ,PRSO ,VEHBIT>\n\t\t<TELL \"You are now in\">\n\t\t<ARTICLE ,PRSO T>\n\t\t<TELL \".\" CR>\n\t\t<MOVE ,WINNER ,PRSO>\n\t\t<COND (<NOT <EQUAL? ,HERE ,SPEEDBOAT>>\n\t\t       <SETG LYING-DOWN T>)>\n\t\t<APPLY <GETP ,PRSO ,P?ACTION> ,M-ENTER>\n\t\t<SET OHERE <>>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"You can't get into\">\n\t\t<ARTICLE ,PRSO T>\n\t\t<TELL \"!\" CR>)>>"
