   "value": "<PLTABLE \"It slips through your fumbling fingers and hits the carpet with a\nnerve-shattering bang.\" \"It dances by you like a thing possessed.\" \"You lunge for it, but the room spins nauseatingly away. The floor\ngives you a light tap on the forehead.\" \"You're certainly picking the tough tasks. The floor acts like a\ntrampoline on an ice rink, or like something they've been working\non for years at Disneyland.\">"
